# Scene: Yellow Plane and Magenta Sphere

# Ambient Light: ratio, color (R,G,B)
A  0.2 255,255,255

# Camera: view point, orientation vector, field-of-view
C  0,2,-5   0,0,1   70

# Light: position, brightness, color (R,G,B)
# Moved light in front and above so it illuminates the visible side
L  -5,5,5   0.8     255,255,255

# --- Objects ---

# Plane: position, normal vector, color (R,G,B)
# This creates a yellow floor.
pl 0,0,0   0,1,0   255,255,0

# Sphere: position, diameter, color (R,G,B)
# This creates a magenta sphere sitting on the plane.
# Center at y=2 so it floats well above the plane (radius=1.0)
sp 0,2,0   2.0     255,0,255